text: The San Sebastián Cathedral (also known as Cathedral of the Good Shepherd)̠ (, ) is a cathedral in San Sebastián, Gipuzkoa, Basque Country, Spain. It is the seat of the suffragan Diocese of San Sebastián and under to the Archdiocese of Pamplona y Tudela. ==Gallery== File:San Sebastian - Catedral 10.jpg|Tower File:Catedral de San Sebastián.jpg|View of the tower-spire of the cathedral File:San Sebastian - Catedral 07.jpg|Apse File:San Sebastian - Catedral 17.jpg|Header File:San Sebastian - Catedral 27.jpg|Altarpiece of the Sacred Heart of Jesus File:San Sebastian - Catedral 32.jpg|Organ ==Notes== == Bibliography == * == Other websites == * Descriptive form on Donostiasansebastian.com Category:Roman Catholic cathedrals in Spain Category:Gipuzkoa Category:1897 establishments in Europe Category:Buildings and structures completed in the 19th century
